Class ObjectList

java.lang.Object
  ObjectList
All Implemented Interfaces:
ObjectListInterface
public class ObjectList
extends java.lang.Object
implements ObjectListInterface

Class ObjectList utilizes the ObjectListNode class and has various return and get functions but its primary function is to keep and maintain pointers to a list of nodes that can grow or shrink in size accordingly during runtime without bounds(other than memory)
